---
target: core
version: 1
validations:
  - name: core-package-exists
    type: file_check
    path: src/core/types.go
    contains:
      - "package core"

  - name: intent-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type Intent struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: validation-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type Validation struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: target-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type Target struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: build-result-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type BuildResult struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: validation-result-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type ValidationResult struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: validation-types-enum
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "file_check\|folder_check\|command_check\|llm_judge" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0
    stdout_contains: ["4"]

  - name: target-status-enum
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "pending\|building\|built\|failed\|outdated" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: core-no-internal-imports
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "github.com/pboueri/intentc/src/" src/core/types.go || echo "0"
    exit_code: 0
    stdout_contains: ["0"]

  - name: core-tests-pass
    type: command_check
    command: go test ./src/core/...
    exit_code: 0

  - name: agent-profile-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type AgentProfile struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: prompt-templates-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type PromptTemplates struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: tool-config-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type ToolConfig struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: schema-violation-type-defined
    type: command_check
    command: grep -c "type SchemaViolation struct" src/core/types.go
    exit_code: 0

  - name: core-types-quality
    type: llm_judge
    rubric: |
      Evaluate the core types package for:
      1. All types from the spec are present with correct fields, including: Intent, Validation, ValidationType, ValidationFile, Target, TargetStatus, BuildResult, ValidationResult, AgentProfile, PromptTemplates, ToolConfig, SchemaViolation
      2. Types are JSON/YAML serializable (appropriate struct tags)
      3. No dependencies on other intentc packages
      4. Follows Go conventions (exported types, godoc-compatible names)
      5. Enum types have const blocks with all specified values
      6. AgentProfile has all fields: Name, Provider, Command, CLIArgs, Timeout, Retries, RateLimit, PromptTemplates, Tools, Skills, ModelID
    severity: error
    context_files: ["src/core/*.go"]
---

# Core Types Validations

These validations ensure the core types package is complete, self-contained, and follows the specification. The core package is the foundation - if it's wrong, everything else breaks. The AgentProfile, PromptTemplates, ToolConfig, and SchemaViolation types are essential for the agent profile system and schema validation features.
